{"type": "article", "id": 19473, "title": "多功能衣架", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-22T07:40:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 45, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702103332fENCptce2PmGSijF.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一个可自由调整结构的木架，包括一个密集排列了圆孔的木框。可以在圆孔的任何地方插入圆柱支架作为挂钩，在两边平行的支架上面搁放一块木板，就构成了一个置物架。它可以是有几排横格的书架，也可以在圆孔上钉上镜子，变成一个多功能的梳妆衣架，放在门边或者钉在墙上，自由而灵活。<a href=\"http://dotdotdot.furniture/collections/build-your-own\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145940VoygR472adkuv3tK.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"1050\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145941wiDMk67KWGuaAmJ0.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"746\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71047619\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145941QYs0SDPdeGk2o3MO.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"800\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.76190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261459421ujA7oVW2zbBGiUP.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"700\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}